Usage: uu2dbu [-help] <value> [ -unit {100 200 400 800 1000 2000 4000 8000 10000 20000}]

-help            # Prints out the command usage
<value>          # specifies value or value list
                 # (float or list of floats, required)
-unit {100 200 400 800 1000 2000 4000 8000 10000 20000}
                 # unit
                 # (enum, optional)